<p>The Virginia Tech Transportation Institute has made headlines with its work on texting and distracted driving research and prevention.</p><ul><li><i>3.1.2013</i> <br />Huffington Post <br /><a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/03/01/ohio-texting-while-driving-ban_n_2792246.html" target="_blank">Ohio texting while driving ban goes into effect</a> (video)</li><li><i>3.19.2013 </i><br />ABC News <br /><a href="http://abcnews.go.com/US/worst-driving-distractions-road-kids/story?id=18684711#.UcMtk_m1F8G" target="_blank">One of the worst driving distractions on the road: Your kids</a></li><li><i>7.28.2009 </i><br />NBC News <br /><a href="http://www.nbcnews.com/id/32185274/ns/technology_and_science-wireless/t/study-texts-while-driving-even-more-dangerous/#.UcM9QPm1F8G" target="_blank">Study: Texts while driving even more dangerous</a></li><li><i>7.27.2009 </i><br />The New York Times <br /><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/28/technology/28texting.html?pagewanted=all&amp;_r=0" target="_blank">In study, texting lifts crash risk by large margin</a></li><li><i>7.28.2009 </i><br />CNN <br /><a href="http://www.cnn.com/2009/TECH/07/28/texting.driving.dangers/" target="_blank">Study: Texting while driving more dangerous for truckers</a><br /></li></ul></div>
